ASoC: sun8i-codec: Convert to SOC_MIXER_ARRAY

SOC_MIXER_ARRAY is a simplified function of SND_SOC_DAPM_MIXER
which handles automatically the ARRAY_SIZE of controls.

Update the driver to use SOC_MIXER_ARRAY.

